snippet.title: Emily is Away ♡ - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Emily is Away 3 is a brand new story set on an old-new social media. Customize your fn profile, send some friend requests and choose your way through this branching narrative.

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/978460/Emily_is_Away_3
Tweet at Emily: https://twitter.com/emerz35
http://emilyisaway.com/
